author: 🎀 leo • ᜇᜆ̥ ᜎᜒᜌᜓ
text: Im afraid when i go back, the pressure of having to find work, elevate my self worth, deal with my abusive relative, and all shit, would get me again into that rabbit hole, i hope i wouldnt, i hope i won’t.

author: 🎀 leo • ᜇᜆ̥ ᜎᜒᜌᜓ
text: My vacation here in leyte helped me to sort of not experience long durations of episodes tho i would still get it even if in the sight of my family members, im just good of looking normal that i dont get noticed.

author: 🎀 leo • ᜇᜆ̥ ᜎᜒᜌᜓ
text: my emotional pain kind of got deepens overtime. It sucks to feel loneliness. it really sucks, i wish to heal from this

author: 🎀 leo • ᜇᜆ̥ ᜎᜒᜌᜓ
text: i kept on reminding that it wasn’t anyones fault to begin with. It just happens. but i hope i could be strong on my own, i hardly get enough social interaction, physically and virtually, and i spiral in that a lot of times.

author: 🎀 leo • ᜇᜆ̥ ᜎᜒᜌᜓ
text: these friends too are also pressured in their own life and work which i deeply empathize but i just kept on being sadder on that fact that i could not connect to some of them like before. was that bad? to even think that way? Or toxic? maybe.

author: 🎀 leo • ᜇᜆ̥ ᜎᜒᜌᜓ
text: my social anxiousness doesn’t help and keeps me very introverted at most in public spaces even i do try to be present. i felt most of the time unwanted. and i felt very needy for always initiating the people i care.

author: 🎀 leo • ᜇᜆ̥ ᜎᜒᜌᜓ
text: i self pity with the amount of rare friends i have, and my inability to connect with people. i do have some close friends and i dont want to blame the circumstances, that people are hustling, and im not special to begin with
